    "body": "the `--rpcaddr` flag is the address of your ethereum node\r\nthe `--rpcport` flag is  the rpc port of your ethereum node\r\nso modify the geth command to:\r\n```\r\ngeth --testnet --datadir /testchain/geth/chaindata --cache 8196 `--rpcport 8545 --rpcaddr X.X.X.3 --rpccorsdomain \"*\" --rpcapi \"eth,net,personal,web3,db,txpool\" --port 35355\r\n```\r\n\r\nthen conntect it like this: (using web3 for example)\r\n```\r\nconst web3 = new Web3('http://X.X.X.3:8545');\r\n```\r\n",
